item.title: CVE-2022-28877|2024-08-03T06:03:53.220Z -- f-secure%20and%20withsecure -- all%20f-secure%20and%20withsecure%20endpoint%20protection%20products%20for%20windows
item.description: This vulnerability allows local user to delete arbitrary file in the system and bypassing security protection which can be abused for local privilege escalation on affected F-Secure & WithSecure windows endpoint products. An attacker must have code execution rights on the victim machine prior to successful exploitation.
